
: build by

podman build -t flan-door -f Dockerfile -- .







: list tools

podman run --rm -- flan-door lister
podman run --rm -- flan-door lister metas dateinner




: show define

podman run --rm -- flan-door helper dateinner
podman run --rm -- flan-door metas helper ask_user







: use before installed

cat | podman run --rm -i -- flan-door proptools t XXX=xxx ...
cat | podman run --rm -i -- flan-door proptools t XXX=xxx ... | podman run --rm -i -- flan-door proptools d -D " "
cat | podman run --rm -i -- flan-door proptools d -D " " | podman run --rm -i -- flan-door proptools t XXX=xxx ...




: install a tool once by installer such as proptools

eval "$(podman run --rm -- flan-door inataller proptools)"

: use if install by installer

cat | proptools t XXX=xxx ...
cat | proptools t XXX=xxx ... | proptools d -D " "
cat | proptools d -D " " | proptools t XXX=xxx ...




: install-out all once

eval "$(podman run --rm -- flan-door cat src.sh)"

: use if install-outed

cat | (proptools t XXX=xxx ...)
cat | (proptools t XXX=xxx ...) | (proptools d -D " ")
cat | (proptools d -D " ") | (proptools t XXX=xxx ...)







: other

还有别的需要就根据汕头的提示自己举一反三吧。应该也够了。。。

: see help use less is suggested

podman run --rm -- s-tool | less

: 不要把这个 readme 当代码交给 SHell 去执行！！！否则你眼前的东西可能会变得妈都不认识了……

